<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Ciena raised to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Ciena raised to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Soundview Financial said analyst Kevin Slocum raised the rating on Ciena Corp to short-term buy from hold, and kept the long-term hold rating.</p>
<p>-- raised the earnings estimates to $0.64 per share from $0.62 for 1997, and to $0.87 from $0.80 for 1998.</p>
<p>-- shares jumped 3-1/8 to 32-1/2.</p>
